data.description: DREAMING OF COUNTRY LIVING? HERE IT IS and MOVE-IN READY - 2.38AC useable level land - Only about 5 miles to Downtown Centralia. Beautiful Customized Home with Fabulous Floorplan, King Sized Primary Ensuite and 2 additional bedrooms on the other end of the home. Enjoy the Large Covered Deck and above ground Pool...ready for Summer Fun and BBQs! Raised Garden Beds and even has a little outbuilding for your farm animals. There is a New Whole House Water Filter, Water Softening System. The Electric Range, Microwave Hood Vent and Deep premium Kitchen Sink are all upgrades and the Island is Granite. Come See for Yourself....and be prepared to FALL IN LOVE!!
